OverHistory.NewCommentry: Matheesha Pathirana to Shubman Gill Wicket
OverHistory.Commentry: Matheesha Pathirana bowling to Shubman Gill, good length ball, pitching on leg stump, Shubman Gill plays an aggressive on drive on the front foot WICKET Shubman Gill lbw Matheesha Pathirana (Gujarat Titans 59 Runs for 1 wickets), Appeal from the fielding side
OverHistory.UPDCommentry:
What an amazing start for the debutant! Gets a big wicket on his first delivery in the IPL! 

Matheesha Pathirana bowling to Shubman Gill, good length ball, pitching on leg stump, The ball slings and Shubman Gill misses the ball. The ball strikes his pads and the umpire raises his hand! Gill takes the review and turns out to be unsuccessful! WICKET!! Shubman Gill lbw Matheesha Pathirana (Gujarat Titans 59 Runs for 1 wickets)
